Third-party software
====================

This product depends on the following third-party Go modules. Full
per-module licenses are reproduced under each module's directory in the
Go module cache. The complete dependency list is in go.mod / go.sum.

- github.com/spf13/cobra (Apache-2.0) — command-line interface framework.
  https://github.com/spf13/cobra
- github.com/spf13/pflag (BSD-3-Clause) — POSIX/GNU-style flag parsing.
  https://github.com/spf13/pflag
- github.com/jackc/pgx/v5 (MIT) — Postgres driver, used to apply packs and
  the shared schema into the target database.
